uote>古典結他 60k<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我果支唔算咩貴野，正常價手工結他<br />\n<br />\n而家仲要好似rosewood禁運，好似又會升<br />\n<br />\n見到有啲人將indian rosewood講到天上有地下無咁真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nP.s 我果支一年出產18-21支<br />\n<br />\n而家訂好似要兩年"},{"pid":"bdef7f4738d33a24da7a3b819cb1f4b05de52d92","tid":82923,"uid":6187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T06:34:48.000Z","msg":"用緊fender american deluxe telecaster，感覺冇standard禁好聲。可能amp廢"},{"pid":"68082e0401d807d490d5402da3028d6ffc4c82db","tid":82923,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T06:57:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古典結他 60k<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01514aa947e01ae929641e0e47565818d097084","tid":82923,"uid":9268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:15:14.000Z","msg":"垃圾sqoe 面單板 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想換taylor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78ed24fd49934309375bd57fecba8c0ab0b8173","tid":82923,"uid":31632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:16:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Epiphone inspired by Texan1964  FT-79 <br />\n音色幾好但唔係太好彈，action 太高</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新手一問:點叫好彈?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為個結他要較大力先㩒到個chord(action), 同埋neck較粗, 高「把」位barre chord 易攰（其實如果成隻歌都 barre應該可以收皮先）個人覺得ibanez個neck做得幾舒服</blockquote><br />\nibanez 啲頸好薄身 唔夠smooth"},{"pid":"90eadb54f99130bdc1e23a14374797c8